    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192670/extras/dea8935c27e03b39a9544b82acb6ff69.avif?t=1769035802\" width=64 height=64 /></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Downcave</strong> is a Roguelite Platformer.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a unique character  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192670/extras/06f1a75b41c60e58799f1e0ad928de38.webp?t=1769035802\" width=50 height=64 /></span> and a planet <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192670/extras/f965f2f8d8c4d9ebba9a22e27ffb8f77.webp?t=1769035802\" width=52 height=52 /></span> to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter stonger enemies  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192670/extras/37d2fd1917a9834aad068949eb74df54.apng?t=1769035802\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192670/extras/37d2fd1917a9834aad068949eb74df54.poster.avif?t=1769035802\" class=\"bb_img\" width=30 height=32 /></picture></span> the deeper you go <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192670/extras/1e8ab49927245744d391e0d01d488985.apng?t=1769035802\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192670/extras/1e8ab49927245744d391e0d01d488985.poster.avif?t=1769035802\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level-up and find more artifacts to power yourself up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192670/extras/f0502085074539a1308be56e2c39cd38.webp?t=1769035802\" width=54 height=44 /></span>  at the end of each run, use gold for permanent upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192670/extras/7002f64f95e68db31d274395e11a855f.webp?t=1769035802\" width=55 height=64 /></span> to be offered 3 random weapons  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192670/extras/5c8d92688d50936407f97066f42c7c21.avif?t=1769035802\" width=64 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can unlock additional inventory slots to carry and wield multiple weapons at once.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is heavily gameplay focused with very little focus on story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Work towards <strong>100%</strong> Completion in the collection log</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
